'''奇瓦瓦沙漠'''（{{lang-en|Chihuahuan Desert}}；{{lang-es|Desierto de Chihuahua, Desierto Chihuahuense}}）是位于墨西哥北部和美国西南部的一片沙漠，面积达{{convert|501,896|km2|0|abbr=on}}<ref name = dinerstein/>，是[[北美洲沙漠列表|北美洲最大的沙漠]]。<ref name=nyt>{{cite book |editor-first=John W. |editor-last=Wright | year=2006 | title=The New York Times Almanac |url=https://archive.org/details/newyorktimes200600wrig | edition=2007 | publisher=Penguin Books | location=New York, New York | isbn=0-14-303820-6 | pages=[https://archive.org/details/newyorktimes200600wrig/page/456 456]}}</ref>

[[世界自然基金会|世界自然基金会]]认为这里是世界上物种多样性最高的沙漠。但由于过度放牧，沙漠环境遭到了极大的破坏<ref name="WWF">{{WWF ecoregion |id=na1303 |name=Chihuahuan desert|accessdate=2010-10-22}}</ref>，很多原生物种的生存空间都已经被[[入侵物种|入侵物种]]挤占，[[墨西哥狼|墨西哥狼]]几乎灭绝<ref>{{cite web|title=Lobos of the Southwest|url=https://mexicanwolves.org/|website=Mexican Wolves|accessdate=20 December 2017|archive-date=2021-02-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210227053948/https://mexicanwolves.org/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。现在该沙漠约7%的地区为环境保护区。

==气候==
这片沙漠主要是由于[[西马德雷山脉|西马德雷山脉]]和[[东马德雷山脉|东马德雷山脉]]的[[雨影|雨影]]形成的，年降水量平均为{{convert|235|mm|in|abbr=on}}<ref name=NMSU>{{cite web | url = http://ddl.nmsu.edu/chihuahua.html | title = The Chihuahuan Desert | publisher = New Mexico State University | accessdate = February 16, 2013 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121227092714/http://ddl.nmsu.edu/chihuahua.html | archivedate = 2012-12-27 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>。唯一的雨季发生于每年六月到十月初，初冬也有少量的降水<ref name= NMSU /><ref name= NPS1 >{{cite web | url = http://www.nps.gov/cave/naturescience/deserts.htm | title = Chihuahuan Desert | publisher = National Park Service | accessdate = February 16, 2013 | archive-date = 2014-10-14 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141014073027/http://www.nps.gov/cave/naturescience/deserts.htm | dead-url = no }}</ref>。奇瓦瓦沙漠海拔较高，约{{convert|600|-|1675|m|0|abbr=on}}<ref name= EOE >{{cite web | url = http://www.eoearth.org/article/Chihuahuan_desert | title = Chihuahuan Desert | publisher = Encyclopedia of Earth | accessdate = February 16, 2013 | archive-date = 2012-12-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121225180508/http://www.eoearth.org/article/Chihuahuan_desert | dead-url = no }}</ref>，因此夏季并不十分炎热，气温在{{convert|35|to|40|C|F|abbr=on|disp=or}}之间，年均气温为{{convert|24|C|F}}。沙漠北部冬天酷寒，有可能发生雪暴<ref name= NMSU />。

